WEBVTT

NOTE Standzeit = 13–15 Zeichen/Sekunde, pro Zeile maximal 37 Zeichen
Englische Version nicht vergessen! Übersetzen, wenn Zeiten geklärt

00:01.000 --> 00:07.000
For these mini-zines you only need
a sheet of paper and scissors.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
Fold the paper in half, …

00:18.000 --> 00:21.000
then again …

00:28.500 --> 00:31.500
and once more.

00:35.500 --> 00:38.500
Crease it well.

00:40.000 --> 00:44.000
Now reopen the last two folds.

00:45.000 --> 00:50.000
It’s time for a cut, namely
on the closed edge

00:50.200 --> 00:55.000
along the central folding line
up to the middle.

00:57.500 --> 01:05.500
Like this! Finally open the paper,
<01:02.000> fold it lengthwise

01:14.000 --> 01:17.000
and squeeze it in form.

01:20.500 --> 01:23.000
Crimp over the booklet …

01:27.000 --> 01:32.000
and your mini-zine is done!